### 外卖系统完整下单流程 API 测试
### 使用 IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client 或 VS Code REST Client 运行

@base_url = http://localhost:8080
@user_phone = 13800000001
@merchant_phone = 13800000002
@rider_phone = 13800000003

# =====================================================================
# STEP 1: 用户注册/登录
# =====================================================================

### 1.1 发送验证码（开发模式固定为 123456）
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/sms/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{user_phone}}"
}

###

### 1.2 用户登录
# @name userLogin
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{user_phone}}",
  "code": "123456"
}

###
@user_token = {{userLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 1.3 商家登录
# @name merchantLogin
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{merchant_phone}}",
  "code": "123456"
}

###
@merchant_token = {{merchantLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 1.4 骑手登录
# @name riderLogin
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{rider_phone}}",
  "code": "123456"
}

###
@rider_token = {{riderLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

# =====================================================================
# STEP 2: 用户端 - 查看商家和菜单
# =====================================================================

### 2.1 查询附近商家（深圳南山科技园）
GET {{base_url}}/api/merchant/nearby?longitude=113.9305&latitude=22.5292&radius=5000&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### 2.2 查询商家菜单
GET {{base_url}}/api/product/menu/1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

# =====================================================================
# STEP 3: 购物车操作
# =====================================================================

### 3.1 加入购物车 - 麻婆豆腐
POST {{base_url}}/api/order/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": 1,
  "dishId": 1,
  "dishName": "麻婆豆腐",
  "price": 18.00,
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### 3.2 加入购物车 - 白米饭（大碗）
POST {{base_url}}/api/order/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": 1,
  "dishId": 5,
  "dishName": "白米饭",
  "price": 2.00,
  "spec": "大碗",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 3.3 查询购物车
GET {{base_url}}/api/order/cart?merchantId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

# =====================================================================
# STEP 4: 提交订单
# =====================================================================

### 4.1 提交订单
# @name submitOrder
POST {{base_url}}/api/order/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": 1,
  "addressId": 1,
  "payType": 1,
  "remark": "不要太辣",
  "items": [
    { "dishId": 1, "quantity": 1, "spec": null },
    { "dishId": 5, "quantity": 2, "spec": "大碗" }
  ]
}

###
@order_no = {{submitOrder.response.body.$.data.orderNo}}

# =====================================================================
# STEP 5: 支付
# =====================================================================

### 5.1 创建支付单
# @name createPayment
POST {{base_url}}/api/pay/create
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNo": "{{order_no}}",
  "payType": 1
}

###
@payment_no = {{createPayment.response.body.$.data.paymentNo}}

### 5.2 模拟支付回调（支付成功）
POST {{base_url}}/api/pay/mock-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentNo": "{{payment_no}}",
  "success": true
}

###

### 5.3 查询支付状态
GET {{base_url}}/api/pay/status/{{order_no}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

# =====================================================================
# STEP 6: 商家端 - 接单和出餐
# =====================================================================

### 6.1 商家查询待处理订单
GET {{base_url}}/api/order/merchant/list?merchantId=1&status=2&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{merchant_token}}

###

### 6.2 商家接单
POST {{base_url}}/api/order/merchant/{{order_no}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{merchant_token}}

###

### 6.3 商家出餐完成（触发派单）
POST {{base_url}}/api/order/merchant/{{order_no}}/ready
Authorization: Bearer {{merchant_token}}

###

# =====================================================================
# STEP 7: 骑手端 - 配送
# =====================================================================

### 7.1 骑手上线并更新位置
PUT {{base_url}}/api/delivery/rider/status
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

###

### 7.2 骑手上报位置（商家附近）
POST {{base_url}}/api/delivery/rider/location
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "longitude": 113.9310,
  "latitude": 22.5298
}

###

### 7.3 骑手确认送达
POST {{base_url}}/api/delivery/order/{{order_no}}/delivered
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}

###

# =====================================================================
# STEP 8: 用户端 - 查询订单
# =====================================================================

### 8.1 查询我的订单列表
GET {{base_url}}/api/order/my?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### 8.2 查询订单详情
GET {{base_url}}/api/order/detail/{{order_no}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

# =====================================================================
# STEP 9: 文件上传测试
# =====================================================================

### 9.1 上传头像（需要替换为实际文件路径）
# POST {{base_url}}/api/file/avatar
# Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
#
# --boundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.jpg"
# Content-Type: image/jpeg
#
# < ./test-avatar.jpg
# --boundary--

# =====================================================================
# STEP 10: 退款流程
# =====================================================================

### 10.1 申请退款
POST {{base_url}}/api/pay/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNo": "{{order_no}}",
  "reason": "不想要了"
}

###

# =====================================================================
# 管理端接口
# =====================================================================

### 管理员 - 查询商家列表
GET {{base_url}}/api/admin/merchant/list?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{merchant_token}}

###

### 管理员 - 审核商家
PUT {{base_url}}/api/admin/merchant/1/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{merchant_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true,
  "reason": ""
}

###
